# Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Check Server Status
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get Story List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stories

### Create Story
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stories
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "First Story",
    "content": "This is the first story using Story Protocol.",
    "author": "Author1",
    "metadata": {
        "genre": "Fantasy",
        "tags": ["web3", "blockchain"]
    }
}

### Get Specific Story
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stories/1

### Update Story
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stories/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "Updated Story Title",
    "content": "This is the updated story content.",
    "metadata": {
        "genre": "SF",
        "tags": ["web3", "blockchain", "AI"]
    }
}

### Delete Story
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stories/1

